      <title>欧洲央行行长拉加德：降息需谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecbs-lagarde-we-need-be-cautious-cutting-rates-2024-10-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德周三表示，欧洲央行在决定进一步降息时需要谨慎，并从未来数据中获取指引。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecbs-lagarde-we-need-be-cautious-cutting-rates-2024-10-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 15:42:04 GMT</pubDate>
